{
  "stem": "14292.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 20.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that-- that I-- our accommodation was reasonable; the food was not too generous, but it was available.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But then they set up a room for the sick people, and it was an absolutely, unbelievably, generously supplied rooms.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they had deluxe items-- which was even for the German that are not too easily available-- like chocolate, or compote, or things like that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was a doctor who asked me to go there to this place, to this room, and I refused.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I refused it, because, you know, that experience I mentioned to you-- these men were describing the first way the peoples put in the trains.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I couldn't believe that the Germans want to do good things with us-- so that I was very suspicious.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't want to be with the sick people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "About two, three days later, it was 29 person in this specific room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And two trucks arrive with SS drivers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they said that they are going to take these people to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the doctor again called me and said that you are-- this was from the first sick ones-- please go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I said that no, I don't want to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it was a lot of people who happily volunteered, but only so-called one lucky one who went in there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we learned later they were shot at the edge of the village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- then from there on-- here again, is a couple of interesting thing which is interesting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a-- for example, at that time, of course, we were all together with women, and children, and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not only the men anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
